<textBlocks>
	<container id="formVBox">
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="25.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Learn about group dynamics and vulnerability">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Summary: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="In this activity you will work through a survival scenario to simulate how you would react in an emergency.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="The scenario tests your teamwork skills, decision making and communication. Following the activity, reflection prompts will help you analyze the group dynamics.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Refer to the survival scenario worksheet. Work with your core team or break into several small groups if you have a larger group. Follow the directions of the scenario. Once the group/s have concluded the survival activity, have a group discussion following the provided prompts.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
	</container>
